description:
Who are the children who will inherit eternal life? What can we learn about Christs church from a typological study of barren women in the Bible? How do the barren, then blessed, women in the Bible contrast with the woman who denies any loss of children? 

Walter Veith explores typological stories about Christ and His bride in this presentation. Study the lives of barren women in the Bible in Christs lineage and be encouraged by the miraculous saving grace of God.

http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/media/1190/1018-more-are-the-children-of-the-barren-woman/
